description:
The rules of the game are simple - you need to throw the ball so as to break all the glasses on the playing field.

But since the ball obeys all the laws of physics, this task can become quite difficult. With each level, the number of obstacles will grow and you will have to strain your accuracy and logic before making a throw.

Lots of levels, various obstacles and objects, interesting puzzles - all this will help you get distracted after a hard day and spend time with good use!

GAME FEATURES:
• Excellent warm-up for accuracy and attentiveness;
• Lots of levels with different difficulty;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
